  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Speech Therapy Clinic to Work on Speech Impairment</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will be beneficial to children in our center many of whom are under the Autism Spectrum Disorders and do not have speech. The clinic will also be of great benefit to the others with Cerebral Palsy and Down Syndrome. It will also benefit others not in our center but have speech problems. The Speech Clinic will provide therapy to improve their speech as well as articulation. It will also provide early intervention for people with hearing impairment and other speech-related challenges.</narrative>
  </description>
